    "title": "Directly expose privatekey inverse function",
    "body": "secp256k1.h doesn't include any functionality to get an inverse of a private key.\r\n\r\nI see another project doing it a bit manually after including scalar_impl.h\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/cryptocoinjs/secp256k1-node/blob/e9d38b279a25049a5f4f66f73f06fb2d70868ce6/src/privatekey.cc#L78-L101\r\n\r\n\r\nI'm wonder if it would be a bit more appropriate to expose a privkey_inverse function a bit more directly in secp256k1.h?\r\n\r\nThanks!",
